description: Ladybug BBQ is bringing fantastic food right to you! You'll get BBQ made right when Ladybug comes to feed you and your guests in and around the Nebraska City area. Whether you're after the Beef Brisket, Grilled Pork Loin, St. Louis Style Spare Ribs, or anything else off their menu, you're sure to love it from the very first bite! Perfect for any occasion that calls for excellent eating, Ladybug BBQ is the truck for you!
name: Ladybug BBQ
